00:55:42,620 --> 00:55:43,620
Mi Ran.

801
00:55:44,660 --> 00:55:46,219
Ini Sutradara Ma Dong Chan.

802
00:55:46,790 --> 00:55:48,060
Bisakah kita bertemu?

803
00:55:58,270 --> 00:55:59,299
Di sini.

804
