00:59:33,379 --> 00:59:36,520
Sedang apa kamu di sini? Kamu tahu betapa cemasnya aku?

865
00:59:42,989 --> 00:59:43,989
Nam Tae.

866
00:59:44,899 --> 00:59:47,100
Jika tasmu terikat pada tiang,

867
00:59:47,770 --> 00:59:50,469
